  storyText: "Festers. Everywhere. Armed mostly with gas-powered rock flingers.\nAt\r
    least 10 of them guarding the hangar door. Typical.\n\nCould try punching\r my
    way through. Or sneaking the long way to the emergency exit.\n\nWhat\r should
    I do?\n1. Take them head on - rush the 10 guards.\n2. Sneak my way\r to the emergency
    exit."
